command_description_item: Search cosmetics by name or ID. Special args available
command_description_playlist: Search playlists by name or ID. Special args available
command_description_shop: Shows the actual ingame shop as image
command_description_news: Shows an interactive message with the ingame news (Battle Royale, Creative and Save the World)
command_description_aes: Shows the current AES keys to decrypt game files
command_description_stats: Search a player's statistics. You can search by Epic, PSN or Xbox account
command_description_code: Shows info about a creator code
command_description_upcoming: Shows an interactive message with all the new/upcoming cosmetics
command_description_search: Searches for .uasset files using the BenBot API
command_description_export: Exports .uasset files using the BenBot API
command_description_invite: Let invite the bot to your server
command_description_info: Shows general info of the bot
command_description_settings: For server admins. Let you change the bot settings in your server
